	tag4<lin<skip2<									\
	tag3<convBlock<256,								\
	tag2<hgstack<preprocess<						\
	tag1<input_rgb_image>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>;
```
Is there anything I can do to make this compile?  I've seen examples with ResNets.  This should be possible.  What can I do to make this work?  I'll be grateful for your time.

