1572,IssuesEvent,2015-10-22 18:03:12+00:00,19155959,dagraham/etm-tk,15252455,melnospam,,,opened,&u until when start date but no time,[],[],0,"Why, when doing on Oct 22, for the line:

    ^ Expect to see for Oct 21, not Oct 22 @s Oct 21 2015 @r d &u Oct 22 2015

python etmtk-3.2.16/etm $HOME/python/etm/mytest c  c ddd MMM dd yyyy -w60

gives:
    Wed Oct 21 2015
      ^ Expect to see for Oct 21, not Oct 22
    Thu Oct 22 2015
      ^ Expect to see for Oct 21, not Oct 22

Since the documentation says:

    &u: until  (datetime) Only include repetitions falling **before**

why do I see it for the ""until"" date (Oct 22)?

But note, for the line (adding a time ""8pm"" after the date):

