2123,IssuesEvent,2018-03-29 18:13:57+00:00,20101515,giampaolo/psutil,681260,giampaolo,,,closed,swap_memory is not in bytes on FreeBSD,"[{'id': 101780110, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/giampaolo/psutil/labels/OpSys-FreeBSD', 'name': 'OpSys-FreeBSD', 'color': 'c5def5', 'default': False}, {'id': 101777531, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/giampaolo/psutil/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'fc2929', 'default': True}]",[],5,"Running `psutil.swap_memory` on FreeBSD 10.3 I gives me the following output:

