3651,IssuesEvent,2016-12-05 12:02:20+00:00,29050338,mementum/backtrader,5713511,mementum,,,closed,Vortex indicator,"[{'id': 164799750, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/mementum/backtrader/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}]",[],0,"Hi,

I have checked several trend indicators and the best is Vortex, could you include it in the next release?

Vortex Indicator: http://www.vortexindicator.com/VFX_VORTEX.PDF  

```python
def Vortex(df, n):  
    i = 0  
    TR = [0]  
    while i < df.index[-1]:  
        Range = max(df.get_value(i + 1, 'High'), df.get_value(i, 'Close')) - min(df.get_value(i + 1, 'Low'), df.get_value(i, 'Close'))  
        TR.append(Range)  
        i = i + 1  
    i = 0  
    VM = [0]  
    while i < df.index[-1]:  
        Range = abs(df.get_value(i + 1, 'High') - df.get_value(i, 'Low')) - abs(df.get_value(i + 1, 'Low') - df.get_value(i, 'High'))  
        VM.append(Range)  
        i = i + 1  
    VI = pd.Series(pd.rolling_sum(pd.Series(VM), n) / pd.rolling_sum(pd.Series(TR), n), name = 'Vortex_' + str(n))  
    df = df.join(VI)  
    return df
```
Thanks a lot",{},{}
