4159,IssuesEvent,2018-08-16 13:17:14+00:00,70314805,kyuupichan/electrumx,3319176,kyuupichan,,,closed,Fix coins with coinbase/generation like transactions,"[{'id': 541801232, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw1NDE4MDEyMzI=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/kyuupichan/electrumx/labels/altcoin', 'name': 'altcoin', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': False}]",[],3,"There are coins like PIVX, Decred, Zcoin that use generation outpoints (hash=ZERO, idx=MINUS_1) in normal transactions.

