6571,IssuesEvent,2016-02-03 23:17:45+00:00,5291754,kurttheviking/simple-hipchat-py,6521666,cachrisman,,,opened,doesn't handle unicode messages gracefully,[],[],0,"If I try to use simple-hipchat-py to send a unicode message to a hipchat room I get the following error

