## What have you tried to solve it?
0. My test method is to use cv::getTickCount(). My main purpose is to do a body detection demo on TX2. I trained and tested a model on a windows PC where mxnet ssd is way faster than caffe faster-rcnn (mxnet 20ms vs caffe 35ms). But the result reversed on TX2 (mxnet 180ms vs caffe 45ms). And I have to set environment MXNET_CUDNN_AUTOTUNE_DEFAULT=0 to run the gpu demo. When I set MXNET_CUDNN_AUTOTUNE_DEFAULT to 1 I got the error above.
