7077,IssuesEvent,2017-12-01 20:53:00+00:00,34864402,apache/incubator-mxnet,30911248,mbaijal,47359,apache,opened,MXNet 1.0.0 Release Feedback: Source Headers and License Files,[],[],0,"## Description
This issue is to track the comments from the MXNet 1.0.0 [general vote thread - email](https://mail-archives.apache.org/mod_mbox/incubator-general/201712.mbox/browser)

