7512,IssuesEvent,2016-09-07 14:53:11+00:00,14310815,plone/plonetheme.barceloneta,11072000,1letter,72034,plone,opened,Missing CSS Rule in grid.plone.less - Grid is broken by custom Build,[],[],0,"The following Situation:
I build my custom CSS and use some barceloneta less files, especially the Grid Definitions.

My CSS Less File:
```css
// Core variables and mixins
@import ""++theme++barceloneta/less/variables.plone.less"";
@import ""++theme++barceloneta/less/mixin.clearfix.plone.less"";
@import ""++theme++barceloneta/less/mixin.gridframework.plone.less""; //grid Bootstrap
@import ""++theme++barceloneta/less/mixin.grid.plone.less""; //grid Bootstrap
@import ""++theme++barceloneta/less/normalize.plone.less""; // Reset and dependencies
@import ""++theme++barceloneta/less/grid.plone.less""; //grid Bootstrap

... here my own defs
h1{color:red;}
```

The normal Bootstrap Grid, for Example this:
```html
<div class=""row"">
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
  <div class=""col-md-1"">.col-md-1</div>
</div>
<div class=""row"">
  <div class=""col-md-8"">.col-md-8</div>
  <div class=""col-md-4"">.col-md-4</div>
</div>
<div class=""row"">
  <div class=""col-md-4"">.col-md-4</div>
  <div class=""col-md-4"">.col-md-4</div>
  <div class=""col-md-4"">.col-md-4</div>
</div>
<div class=""row"">
  <div class=""col-md-6"">.col-md-6</div>
  <div class=""col-md-6"">.col-md-6</div>
</div>
```
is broken, because the Definition:
```css
* {
  -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
  -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
*:before,
*:after {
  -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
  -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
```
is missing.
Please add this to [grid.plone.less](https://github.com/plone/plonetheme.barceloneta/blob/master/plonetheme/barceloneta/theme/less/grid.plone.less) or [normalize.plone.less](https://github.com/plone/plonetheme.barceloneta/blob/master/plonetheme/barceloneta/theme/less/normalize.plone.less)",{},{}
