| aggregation level      | per event                       | mean and stddev       |
|-------|---------------------------------|-----------------------|
| **asset** | losses_by_asset_per_event-rlzs  | losses_by_asset-rlzs  |
|       | losses_by_asset_per_event-stats* | losses_by_asset-stats* |
| **taxonomy** | losses_by_taxon_per_event-rlzs  | losses_by_taxon-rlzs  |
|       | losses_by_taxon_per_event-stats* | losses_by_taxon-stats* |
| **portfolio** | losses_total_per_event-rlzs     | losses_total-rlzs     |
|       | losses_total_per_event-stats*    | losses_total-stats*    |

\* Placeholder names in case these outputs are added in future releases",{},{}
