8180,IssuesEvent,2016-08-17 14:19:00+00:00,24774658,boto/boto3,6535531,octalthorpe,327752,boto,opened,ECS - Support for 'host' networking mode,[],[],0,"I appears that setting 'networkMode' to 'host', in an ECS task definition does not end up in the task definition on the AWS side, and defaults back to 'bridge' mode.

