8678,IssuesEvent,2016-01-11 03:46:00+00:00,24757484,robotpy/robotpy-wpilib,567900,virtuald,640276,robotpy,opened,CameraServer doesn't seem to work with 2016 default dashboard,[],[],0,"I just tried out the USBCamera class RobotPy 2016.0.0 with the default LabVIEW dashboard, and it doesn't work. Looking at tcpdump, the RoboRIO seems to be rejecting the incoming connections for some reason.

