8919,IssuesEvent,2015-09-09 19:42:37+00:00,9629438,scrapy/queuelib,37369,dangra,733635,scrapy,closed,scrapy tests fail with queuelib 1.4.0,[],[],2,"Hey @dangra, 

Scrapy tests start to fail after https://github.com/scrapy/queuelib/commit/89f6df01f1dc43b938243d9c3fa3aa75e5dddda2 (see https://travis-ci.org/scrapy/scrapy/jobs/79465256). It looks like a test-only issue: `.qdir` was renamed to `.qpath`.

