11096,IssuesEvent,2016-04-13 16:45:56+00:00,24213271,adobe-type-tools/afdko,2856984,readroberts,2768660,adobe-type-tools,closed,[spec] Missing angle brackets in a example of `valueRecordDef`,[],[],1,"In [section 2.e.v](http://www.adobe.com/devnet/opentype/afdko/topic_feature_file_syntax.html#2.e.v ""OpenType Feature File Specification | Adobe Developer Connection"") of the OpenType Feature File Specification, there is a malformed example:

