11744,IssuesEvent,2018-06-06 16:02:05+00:00,7209075,pantsbuild/pants,70188,sivy,3065172,pantsbuild,opened,Add option to pants.ini and python_binary to change or elide pex binary filename extension,[],[],0,"In some cases it might be preferable for python binaries (pex) to have a different filename extension than "".pex"", or no extension. In discussing this in Slack, it was pointed out that this could be configured globally in `pants.ini` or on a case-by-case basis as a parameter to `pants_binary`.

