13086,IssuesEvent,2015-03-16 17:43:08+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,71486,asmeurer,6392739,conda,opened,Better error message when trying to update a pinned package,[],[],0,"If you try to update a pinned package that you forgot you pinned, the error message tells you that it is already up to date, and it can be very confusing. We should make the error message note that it is pinned if that is the case. ",{},{}
