13867,IssuesEvent,2016-01-17 00:16:55+00:00,18513454,cmusphinx/pocketsphinx,2886672,nshmyrev,7203378,cmusphinx,closed,Setting a maximum listening time,[],[],3,"Is there a way to set a timeout, where it stops and computes what was said even though voice is still happening? The TV really messes with it and all of my commands are no more than 4 words. Meaning if I could set a max timeout at like 5 continuous seconds, that would be nice.",{},{}
