14506,IssuesEvent,2016-04-01 15:04:46+00:00,24245737,projectmesa/mesa,596978,dmasad,8754505,projectmesa,closed,Some issues with the Tutorial: i.e. parameter to get a histogram of agent wealth,[],[],1,"Found some things in the tutorial:
