14591,IssuesEvent,2016-07-07 16:36:28+00:00,45062555,F5Networks/f5-common-python,1444377,jgruber,8935905,F5Networks,opened,Management initialization should allow for connection timeout setting,[],"[{'login': 'zancas', 'id': 640955, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/640955?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/zancas', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/zancas/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}, {'login': 'jgruber', 'id': 1444377, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1444377?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/jgruber', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jgruber/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"The ManagementRoot object allows you to pass a timeout=n kwarg, but it does not pass that kwarg to the get_tmos_version() nor the underlying session.get() request. That leads to situations where only default timeouts are possible with MangaementRoot which won't work.

I added a fix in the feature.bigiq branch.",{},{}
