15033,IssuesEvent,2018-06-20 20:18:34+00:00,9952134,python-visualization/folium,950575,ocefpaf,9969242,python-visualization,closed,Radius Bug,[],[],1,"I think there is a bug in how the radius option is working with Folium.  I have the following code:

