```py
GET api/galleries # list all galleries
GET api/galleries/{id} # fetch a specific gallery
POST api/galleries/ # create a new gallery
PATCH api/galleries/{id} # update an existing gallery
DELETE api/galleries/{id} # delete a gallery
```

The `POST` and `PATCH` methods accept data in the following format:

```json
{
  ""title"": ""Gallery title"",
  ""attachment_json"": [
    {
      ""caption"": ""test caption 1"",
      ""image_id"": 1
    },
