15685,IssuesEvent,2018-02-08 21:11:40+00:00,53168296,level12/webgrid,8727453,guruofgentoo,11673919,level12,opened,add can_render property on renderers,[],[],0,"Some renderers, like Excel, will have inherent limitations such as row counts. We should have a property on the renderer that checks the appropriate criteria and returns True/False.
- calling the renderer when `can_render` is False should raise an exception
