15688,IssuesEvent,2018-06-12 19:30:54+00:00,68161929,oasis-open/cti-stix-validator,1045796,gtback,11744379,oasis-open,closed,the validator should be able to be called as a library method,[],"[{'login': 'clenk', 'id': 402940, 'node_id': 'MDQ6VXNlcjQwMjk0MA==', 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/402940?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/clenk', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/clenk/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"The elevator ""calls"" the stix2 validator as sort of a library.  The elevator should just use the validator via its API (command line args).  Currently, the elevator is parsing the validator's args and setting some of them directly in ValidatorOptions - which should be hidden.

The main method should be rewritten, so you just pass in the command line arg string.  Then the new main method of the validator is just a wrapper around that library method.",{},{}
