<!-- Instructions For Filing a Bug: https://github.com/scikit-learn-contrib/imbalanced-learn/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#filing-bugs -->

#### Description
<!-- Example: Joblib Error thrown when calling fit on LatentDirichletAllocation with evaluate_every > 0-->

The test should use `assert_allclose` instead of `assert_array_almost_equal` as prescribed in the documentation of numpy.

#### Steps/Code to Reproduce
<!--
Example:
```
from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import CountVectorizer
from sklearn.decomposition import LatentDirichletAllocation

