18179,IssuesEvent,2018-02-27 08:33:52+00:00,23465887,pdfminer/pdfminer.six,41628,pudo,22586632,pdfminer,opened,Bounty: fixing up pdfminer(.six),[],[],0,"I work with a non-profit journalism organisation (@occrp) where we do a lot of PDF mining. In the past, working with `pdfminer` has proven challenging, the project needs a good cleanup. To that end, I'd like to offer up two or three months of (remote) contracting work for someone who can:

