* Inserting OCRd text into documents and saving an extended version to PDF/A
* Down-sampling images in PDFs to a lower resolution

Email: pudo@occrp.org. We're a US-based 501(c)3 corp.

Excuse me for spamming the bug tracker, I will close this in 7 days to keep the issues clean.",{},{}
