18335,IssuesEvent,2017-04-12 18:53:57+00:00,34138622,jupyter-widgets/ipywidgets,192614,jasongrout,25869250,jupyter-widgets,closed,Snapshot widget state when syncing,"[{'id': 200981683, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/jupyter-widgets/ipywidgets/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'b60205', 'default': True}]",[],26,"# Summary

We should snapshot the widget state when syncing state from the frontend to the kernel, since the sync may happen asynchronously because of the throttling.

---
# Original issue

hi

we have simple code in `nglview` that works fine with `ipywidgets 5.2.2`.
However, there is no effect if using `mode.set(...)` in `6.0.0.beta5` version.

